lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur striker Harry Kane has been backed to rediscover his scoring touch by manager Mauricio Pochettino ahead of Wednesday's Premier League visit to Southampton.

headline.print_headline: Pochettino Not Worried by Kane Drought Ahead of Saints Trip
